collectible.name: Voxeth DR-1138 Torso Replacement
collectible.description:
Since the first voxel, It has been known that Cryptovoxiens do not require breathing, We all do not really need to consume vood...We just pretend. From this we sometimes replace our body parts with dragon fangs, computer parts, Sports cars or even entire voxnimals. Well here at Voxeth,  We do not condone replacing ones body parts with voxnimals, They are too cute, Rare and you are selfish to want to assimilate their beauty into your form you sick bastard! So why not keep it basic. An entire torso built specifically to mine $COLR

NOTE: This is NOT the recalled version. We guarantee this version will NOT explode. We promise.
(quality not guaranteed, No refunds, Limited quantities, 3-day warranty, Call now.)

collectible.name: Voxeth DR-404 Cranial Replacement
collectible.description: Ever... Just want to see the world? No, Literally.. Everyone knows Cryptovoxlians have no eyes, they must be installed into ones cranium. A terrible fact, Anywho! Why go through all the effort of shaping a face when you can replace your entire head! Suggested by the janitor here at Voxeth labs during a drunken night of cryptopoker and a few too many. After a horrible operation we can install this state of the art DR-404 V.2 model in place of your head and you will enjoy vision in the form of a cheap 1980's color TV.
